# Architecture Guidelines

## Project Type: Next.js Pages Router



### Monorepo Structure (pnpm)

Workspaces:
- `apps\api` - @guardrail/api
- `apps\web-ui` - @guardrail/web-ui
- `packages\ai-guardrails` - @guardrail/ai-guardrails
- `packages\cli` - guardrail-cli
- `packages\compliance` - @guardrail/compliance
- `packages\core` - guardrail-core
- `packages\database` - @guardrail/database
- `packages\security` - guardrail-security

Shared Packages:
- typescript (used in 9 workspaces)
- @types/node (used in 8 workspaces)
- zod (used in 4 workspaces)
- vitest (used in 4 workspaces)
- guardrail-core (used in 3 workspaces)


### Directory Purpose
- `src/` - Source code root
- `src/pages/` - Project files
- `src/components/` - Project files
- `src/lib/` - Project files
- `src/services/` - Project files
- `src/server/` - Project files
- `prisma/` - Database schema and migrations

### Import Aliases
- Use `@/` for src directory imports
- Never use relative imports deeper than `../`
